<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hiltpolt von Fraunberg</head><p>Der Rat mahnt wegen des längst versprochenen Schuldbriefs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_497" id="248r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_497_r1l2"><expan>Hılpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_497_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hılpolt / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / . <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des briefs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l5"> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / den Jr vns gevertigt ſolt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_497_line_1592412603087_29"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> / <expan>Daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_497_r1l4">wir </ab></add> nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l7"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / . dann daʒ Jr vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_497_r1l6">vor her </ab></add> vmb gefüret habt vnd noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l8">vmbcʒefüren maint / . Nu getraw vvir ew vvol Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigt</expan> den brief noch vnd halt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_497_r1l9">vns </ab></add> als es geteydingt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l11">ıſt <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo / daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew nicht lenger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_497_r1l12">vmbgefürt werden / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_497" id="248r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hilpolt, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des briefs
                        <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, den ir uns gevertigt solt
                                    <add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan></add>
<expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>
<add>wir</add> nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, dann daz ir uns
                            <add>vorher</add> umbgefüret habt und noch umbczefüren maint. Nu getraw
                        wir ew wol, ir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigt</expan> den brief noch und halt
                            <add>uns</add>, als es geteydingt ist <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        also daz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew nicht lenger umbgefürt werden.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la.</expan></ab>
</div>
